    <h2 class="section-title">Essential Microservices Patterns</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">These patterns from Chris Richardson's microservices.io solve the hard distributed systems problems — data consistency, service resiliency, and observability.</p>
    <div class="card-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(290px,1fr));text-align:left;">

