      </div>
      <div class="card" style="border-color:rgba(74,222,128,0.35);">
        <div class="card-icon" style="background:rgba(74,222,128,0.12);">&#9881;&#65039;</div>
        <div class="badge badge-green" style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">12factor.net &middot; Adam Wiggins &middot; 2011</div>
        <h3>The Twelve-Factor App</h3>
        <p style="margin:0.75rem 0 0.5rem;">Drafted by Heroku engineers from observations running thousands of SaaS apps: a methodology for building <strong style="color:var(--text-primary);">cloud-native applications</strong> that maximize portability, deployability, and scalability.</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:0.75rem;">12 factors &middot; Codebase &#8594; Build &#8594; Release &#8594; Run &middot; Stateless processes &middot; Config in environment</p>
