          <p style="color:var(--text-primary);font-size:0.88rem;"><strong style="color:var(--accent-red);">&#10007; Not quite.</strong> The canonical definition: "a suite of small services, each running in its own process and communicating with lightweight mechanisms, often an HTTP resource API." <em style="color:var(--text-muted);">&#8212; martinfowler.com/articles/microservices.html (2014)</em></p>
        </div>
